name: Eternal Warrior Helm
description: During the Renaissance ages of Lore, many of kings found enjoyment in the sport of combat. Pitting combatants against one another, the kings fitted their fighters with the best of armors that Lore had to offer. The Eternal Warriors realized that these armors are still the greatest that man has ever made so they came in like a thief in the night and "borrowed" them. ARE YOU NOT ENTERTAINED?!?!
